EASTERN NORTH ATLANTIC.
SCOTLAND.
DNC 19.
1. HAZARDOUS OPERATIONS 150800Z TO 191800Z OCT
   IN AREA WITHIN 55 MILES OF 57-22.4N 009-10.6W.
   VESSELS INTENDING TO ENTER AREA SHOULD
   CONTACT HEBRIDES RANGE CONTROL ON VHF CH 16
   OR PHONE: 187 060 4449 FOR ADVICE.
2. CANCEL THIS MSG 191900Z OCT 19.
